description:
--Note-- this LoRA tests results wasn't that great, it was locked in the archive for some time , so here it is for what it's worth.

MUK-MonsieuR - Artist Style 🎨

This Lora is trained on the style of MUK(むっく)／MonsieuR, you can checkout their creations on Pixiv Fanbox [may contain extreme explicit content!!].

Usage Tips :

  • regular use is at the weight of 1 to 0.7 ,

  • adding mukartistto the prompt will force the image to subject covered by the artist while giving the LoRA a bit more influence.

  • try experimenting with adding "realistic" or "lineart" to explore variations of the style.
